  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      A study to assess the safety and efficacy of the addition of sitagliptin compared to placebo
      in patients with Type 2 Diabetes Mellitus who have inadequate glycemic control on metformin.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
